beer.beer_description:
At Crown we are committed to using only the finest Australian ingredients. Brewed using 100% Australian malt and a combination of Galaxy® and Pride of Ringwood hops, our Brew Masters have crafted a refreshing, truly Australian-style ale with citrus and floral aromas and a sweet maltiness.

Our Golden Ale is a refined and easy-drinking beer, to be enjoyed chilled on any occasion with your closest friends.

With a subtle nod to the very 'on-trend' floral/citrus aromas (built via the inclusion of 'galaxy hops'). Crown Golden Ale is balanced perfectly against the soft, caramel notes of the crystal and roasted malts.

Crown Golden Ale retains the signature Australian ingredients of Crown Lager:

CA1 grade malt and first choice Pride of Ringwood hops.

To create 'Australia's finest' beers we only use the finest Australian ingredient
